    <div class="container">
        <h1>The Chemical Song</h1>
        <h2>(Tune: "Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star")</h2>
        
        <p><strong>NH<sub>4</sub>Cl</strong> and <strong>CH<sub>2</sub>O</strong>,<br>
        Mix them well and watch it grow!</p>
        
        <p><strong>H<sub>2</sub>C == N</strong> and <strong>HCOOH</strong>,<br>
        Reacts so fast, it's quite a show!</p>
        
        <p><strong>H<sub>2</sub>C == N</strong> plus <strong>CH<sub>2</sub>O</strong>,<br>
        Water joins, now let it flow.</p>
        
        <p>NaOH comes in to play,<br>
        <strong>H<sub>3</sub>C --- NH<sub>2</sub></strong> is here to stay!</p>
        
        <p><strong>C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>Cl</strong>,<br>
        Add NaCN, that's the drill.</p>
        
        <p><strong>C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>CN</strong>,<br>
        And NaCl shows up again!</p>
        
        <p>Boil it down, take it away,<br>
        <strong>C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>COOH</strong> to stay.</p>
        
        <p>Phenylacetic Acid bright,<br>
        Forms so fast, it's quite a sight!</p>
        
        <p><strong>CH<sub>3</sub>COCl</strong> plus <strong>C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>3</sub>NaO<sub>2</sub></strong>,<br>
        Makes <strong>C<sub>4</sub>H<sub>6</sub>O<sub>3</sub></strong> in a fix!</p>
        
        <p>Acetic Anhydride now,<br>
        See it form and take a bow!</p>
        
        <p><strong>C<sub>4</sub>H<sub>6</sub>O<sub>3</sub></strong> plus <strong>C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>COOH</strong>,<br>
        Forms <strong>C<sub>9</sub>H<sub>10</sub>O</strong> so good!</p>
        
        <p>Phenylacetone appears,<br>
        Almost done, the end is near!</p>
        
        <p><strong>C<sub>9</sub>H<sub>10</sub>O</strong> plus <strong>H<sub>3</sub>C --- NH<sub>2</sub></strong><br>
        <strong>C<sub>10</sub>H<sub>15</sub>N</strong> is here, it's true!</p>
        
        <p>Let it sit, now watch it stay,<br>
        Sing again another day!</p>
    </div>
